text: President @jokowi announced that #Indonesia received 1.2 mln dosage of #China's #COVID19 #vaccine made by Sinovac Biatech Ltd. ystd (6/12) as the govt prepares a mass inoculation program. According to the arrangement, another 1.8 mln will be received by the end of 2020. https://t.co/rAuGhGukXE
